== 历史 ==
苹果最早在2013年6月10日的的WWDC上将这种iOS功能在汽车上的延伸称作“车载iOS”（iOS in the Car），<ref name="keynote"/>不过开发过程中该项目的代码为Stark。[[iOS版本历史#7.1|iOS 7.1]]的Beta 1与2版包含了一些关于iOS不久后运行于汽车中的细节，暗示了它将很快被发布。<ref name="9to5 soon released 1">{{cite web|url=http://9to5mac.com/2013/12/13/ios-7-1-likely-to-unlock-apples-upcoming-ios-in-the-car-feature|title=iOS 7.1 likely to unlock Apple’s upcoming iOS in the Car feature|publisher=[[Apple_community#9to5Mac|9to5Mac]]|first=Michael|last=Steeber|date=2013-12-13|accessdate=2013-12-13|archive-date=2013-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213224434/http://9to5mac.com/2013/12/13/ios-7-1-likely-to-unlock-apples-upcoming-ios-in-the-car-feature/|dead-url=no}}</ref>根据2014年1月的媒体报道，车载iOS的发布由于苹果自身的企划问题而被推迟，主要是由于其管理团队“并不完全确定”在软件方面的下一步计划，而开发团队不得不为了在WWDC上的展示时间而“竭力游说”之。<ref name="AI release strife 1">{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/14/01/28/organizational-strife-said-to-bedevil-apples-ios-in-the-car-intiative|title=Organizational strife said to bedevil Apple's iOS in the Car initiative|publisher=[[Apple_community#AppleInsider|AppleInsider]]|first=Shane|last=Cole|date=2014-01-28|accessdate=2014-01-28|archive-date=2014-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140130072432/http://appleinsider.com/articles/14/01/28/organizational-strife-said-to-bedevil-apples-ios-in-the-car-intiative|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年3月3日，苹果通过向媒体发放新闻稿以及更新官方网站的页面来宣布先前的车载iOS服务已更名为CarPlay，同时也声称有更多的制造商愿意藉此整合未来的汽车，且CarPlay能够与iPhone最新的三个版本（[[iPhone_5S|5S]]、[[iPhone_5C|5C]]与[[iPhone_5|5]]）搭配使用。<ref name="9to5 CP announced 1">{{cite web|url=http://9to5mac.com/2014/03/03/apple-rebrands-ios-in-the-car-as-carplay-compatible-vehicles-launching-later-this-year|title=Apple rebrands iOS in the Car as CarPlay, compatible vehicles launching later this year|publisher=[[Apple_community#9to5Mac|9to5Mac]]|first=Benjamin|last=Mayo|date=2014-03-03|accessdate=2014-03-03|archive-date=2016-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160413000628/http://9to5mac.com/2014/03/03/apple-rebrands-ios-in-the-car-as-carplay-compatible-vehicles-launching-later-this-year/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Apple PR CP announced 1">{{cite web|url=http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2014/03/03Apple-Rolls-Out-CarPlay-Giving-Drivers-a-Smarter-Safer-More-Fun-Way-to-Use-iPhone-in-the-Car.html|title=Apple Rolls Out CarPlay Giving Drivers a Smarter, Safer & More Fun Way to Use iPhone in the Car|publisher=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple]]|date=2014-03-03|accessdate=2014-03-03|archive-date=2014-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140304081905/http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2014/03/03Apple-Rolls-Out-CarPlay-Giving-Drivers-a-Smarter-Safer-More-Fun-Way-to-Use-iPhone-in-the-Car.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年9月推出的[[iOS_12|iOS 12]]所內建之CarPlay開始支援第三方導航程式，例如[[Google_Map|Google Map]]，提供導航使用者更多選擇。

